<br>
One attack every 7 or 8 seconds for 41 points damage (magic number with ragebringer at level 60) vs 31 points damage (magic number with bloodpoint at level 60) = losing 10'ish damage or so on your frontstabs that come every 7-8 seconds.  If you're soloing, and have a high dex, I think you'd come out ahead with the proc's vs the extra 10 points of damage or so per frontstab.  Yes, however you parse it ragebringer's gonna come out ahead in the pure damage, but only if you live through the entire fight, which is what the proc on the bloodpoint allows you to do. <p><p><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=37752">Darkrok Shadowwalker</a> - Redeemed <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/data/item.asp?Id=1926">Epicfied</a> Dwarven Rogue of <img src="http://www.templeofdawneq.com/templeofdawn/pictures/darkrok-level.gif"> Missions
